     CRYPTOGRAPHY
 It is the practice and study of techniques for securing communication and data protection.It is used to enhance confidentiality,integrity and authenticity.

Symmetric and Assymetric:
   Symmetric(Private key Cryptography)
It uses the same key to encrypt and decrypt the data.
keeping the private key secret is very important.
eg: DES-Data Encryption Standard
    AES-Advanced Encryption Standard

Assymetric(Public key cryptography)
It uses same key for encryption and decryption, it uses a pair of key,Publickey to encrypt and private key to decrypt
It uses RSA(Rivest,Shamir,Adleman)
RSA is very secure

